The final project for Computer Graphics, Interterm 2009.
Chapman University
Joe Smith

A relatively simple trial of various opengl features.

CONTROLS
-----------
Q - Quit
K - Launch Missile
Left Click - Launch Missile
Arrow Keys - Maneuver Jet

Texture Mapping - Tux on the wings (Skybox)
Blending - Flames/Explosion/Cockpit
Clipping - Cockpit (Sphere + Cylinder + Sphere)
Mouse + Keyboard Control - Rockets/Movement
Menu - Different Views

Skybox graphics from http://www.freebasic.net/forum/viewtopic.php?p=110440
Code for loading bitmaps and getting it to run (only a few tweaks for my stuff) http://nehe.gamedev.net/data/lessons/lesson.asp?lesson=06
